Class MessageType

  • java.lang.Object
    • commInfra.MessageType

  • public class MessageType
extends java.lang.Object
    Type of the exchanged messages. the Implementation of a client-server model of type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
